parameters:
\c[27]\n<Rio>"Hah...! Hah...! Ugh...guh...ugh..., this
is...definitely...some kind of...mis...take..."

\c[27]Dragged into the nest of the worms, Rio is
restrained by her limbs, completely immobilized...

\c[27]Her belly, swollen like that of a pregnant
woman in a short time, writhes ominously from the
inside...

\c[27]\n<Rio>"Ugh...hic...ugh..., it's moving...stop...I don't
want it...to be born..."

\c[27]As Rio lets out a voice of desperate
pleading, "something" mocks her by crawling from
her womb to her vagina, and then out of her
body...!

\c[27]\n<Rio>"Aghh! Gih! No, no good...eh! It's coming out...!
Giving birth to...a monster's...child..."

\c[27]A young creature of the monster is born from
inside Rio.

\c[27]Impregnated and forced to give birth, even
the strong-willed Rio despairs, trembling and
screaming...

\c[27]\n<Rio>"Agh...no...not anymore...don't be
born...hic...ugh, inside my stomach...it's still
moving...ughh!\i[93]"

\c[27]Following the first one, a second and a
third...one after another, the worm's offspring
crawl out of Rio's body...

\c[27]Unable to move and without any means to
resist, Rio can only watch the ghastly scene
unfolding before her eyes...

\c[27]After a while, covered in the creatures she
has given birth to, she continues to give birth to
one after another...

\c[27]Eventually, all hope fades from her eyes,
and Rio even begins to find a twisted pleasure in
the act of birthing monsters...

\c[27]\n<Rio>"Haa-...haa-...\i[93]Again...it's being
born...uhh\i[93]Ah...haa...giving birth to
monsters feels...goodd...\i[93]"

\c[27]Her body convulses as she quietly reaches
climax while continuing to give birth to monsters.

\c[27]The worm, having understood how to
impregnate, watches Rio with gleaming eyes as she
continues to give birth...

\c[27]Exposing its reproductive organ from its
body to plant its seed again, it slowly approaches
Rio once more...

The flames are burning fiercely. They don't seem
to be going out anytime soon.
